{"id":2134,"date":"2020-09-28T18:00:46","date_gmt":"2020-09-28T17:00:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/?post_type=module&#038;p=2134"},"modified":"2020-09-28T12:21:53","modified_gmt":"2020-09-28T11:21:53","slug":"link-building-for-local-sites","status":"publish","type":"module","link":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/module\/local-seo\/link-building-for-local-sites","title":{"rendered":"Link Building For Local Sites"},"featured_media":0,"parent":418,"menu_order":88,"template":"","acf":{"module_quiz":"","module_time":"6","module_difficulty":{"value":"easy","label":"Easy"},"module_short_description":"<p>A closer look at how to build links for local websites.<\/p>\n","module_long_description":"<p>We take a quick look at three link building techniques for Local SEO.<\/p>\n","video_file":false,"video_url":"","content":"<p>As is the case with organic SEO, links are a huge ranking signal for local search.<\/p>\n<p>Let\u2019s take a closer look at ways you can build links for your local website.<\/p>\n<h2>Local Citations<\/h2>\n<p>Local Citations are essentially just online mentions of your business. They usually display your business name, address, and phone number aka NAP (Name, Address, Phone).<\/p>\n<p>Although GMB is the most important business citation for local SEO there are lots of other important ones that you should look at getting too such as:<\/p>\n<div class=\"list-styles list-styles__circle list-styles__circle--primary-color\"><ul>\n<li>Facebook<\/li>\n<li>Yelp<\/li>\n<li>Angie\u2019s List<\/li>\n<li>Yellow Pages<\/li>\n<li>Citysearch<\/li>\n<li>Foursquare<\/li>\n<li>TripAdvisor<\/li>\n<li>Apple Maps<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<p>A structured citation contains NAP information that is presented in a visually-structured manner like a business directory.<\/p>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2135\" src=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-NAP.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"801\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-NAP.png 801w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-NAP-103x40.png 103w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-NAP-205x80.png 205w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-NAP-77x30.png 77w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-NAP-154x60.png 154w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-NAP-62x24.png 62w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-NAP-123x48.png 123w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-NAP-46x18.png 46w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-NAP-92x36.png 92w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 801px) 100vw, 801px\" \/>\n<p>An unstructured citation contains the same or similar information about your business, but in an unstructured format like a blog post or article.<\/p>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2136\" src=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-unstructured-citation.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1266\" height=\"396\" srcset=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-unstructured-citation.png 1266w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-unstructured-citation-128x40.png 128w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-unstructured-citation-256x80.png 256w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-unstructured-citation-96x30.png 96w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-unstructured-citation-192x60.png 192w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-unstructured-citation-77x24.png 77w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-unstructured-citation-153x48.png 153w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-unstructured-citation-58x18.png 58w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-LC-unstructured-citation-115x36.png 115w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1266px) 100vw, 1266px\" \/>\n<p>Building local citations is incredibly easy &#8211; to start you off, here\u2019s <a href=\"https:\/\/whitespark.ca\/top-local-citation-sources-by-country\/united-states\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">50 of the core U.S. citations<\/a> courtesy of Whitespark.<\/p>\n<p>If you aren\u2019t based in the United States, don\u2019t worry &#8211; you can find the top citation sources for your country <a href=\"https:\/\/whitespark.ca\/top-local-citation-sources-by-country\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">here<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Later on in this module, we\u2019ll show how you can find and audit your local citations.<\/p>\n<h2>Guest Posts on Local Blogs<\/h2>\n<p>Guest blogging is and always has been one of the most common and effective ways to build high-quality links.<\/p>\n<p>That being said, the purpose with this method is to build exposure by creating content for blogs that have the potential to send referral traffic to your website.<\/p>\n<p>In this case, you should look for local blogs and publications that (ideally) are specific to your niche or industry.<\/p>\n<p>Google search operators are great for doing this!<\/p>\n<div class=\"list-styles list-styles__circle list-styles__circle--primary-color\"><ul>\n<li>[location] intitle:\u201dwrite for us\u201d<\/li>\n<li>[location] intitle:\u201dwrite for me\u201d<\/li>\n<li>[location] inurl:\u201dwrite-for-us<\/li>\n<li>[location] inurl:\u201dwrite-for-me\u201d<\/li>\n<li>[location] \u201dwrite for us\u201d<\/li>\n<li>[location] \u201dguest post\u201d<\/li>\n<li>[location] \u201csubmit an article\u201d<\/li>\n<li>[industry \/ niche] intitle:\u201dwrite for us\u201d<\/li>\n<li>[industry \/ niche] intitle:\u201dwrite for me\u201d<\/li>\n<li>[industry \/ niche] inurl:\u201dwrite-for-us\u201d<\/li>\n<li>[industry \/ niche] inurl:\u201dwrite-for-me\u201d<\/li>\n<li>[industry \/ niche] \u201dwrite for us\u201d<\/li>\n<li>[industry \/ niche] \u201dguest post\u201d<\/li>\n<li>[industry \/ niche] \u201csubmit an article\u201d<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<p>Here\u2019s an example of location based search:<\/p>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2137\" src=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-lbs.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"995\" height=\"647\" srcset=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-lbs.png 995w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-lbs-62x40.png 62w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-lbs-123x80.png 123w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-lbs-46x30.png 46w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-lbs-92x60.png 92w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-lbs-37x24.png 37w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-lbs-74x48.png 74w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-lbs-28x18.png 28w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-lbs-55x36.png 55w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px\" \/>\n<p>Here\u2019s an example of an industry based search:<\/p>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2138\" src=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-ibs.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"995\" height=\"665\" srcset=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-ibs.png 995w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-ibs-60x40.png 60w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-ibs-120x80.png 120w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-ibs-45x30.png 45w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-ibs-90x60.png 90w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-ibs-36x24.png 36w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-ibs-72x48.png 72w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-ibs-27x18.png 27w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-GPoLB-ibs-54x36.png 54w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 995px) 100vw, 995px\" \/>\n<h2>Steal From Your Competitors<\/h2>\n<p>It goes without saying that one of the most effective ways to quickly find linking opportunities, is to look at your competitors.<\/p>\n<p>Ahrefs has a useful feature for this called <a href=\"https:\/\/ahrefs.com\/link-intersect\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Link Intersect<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>To identify your top competitors, simply do a search on Google for your core keywords like \u201cplumbers surrey\u201d or \u201cwedding photographer leicester\u201d.<\/p>\n<p>All you have to do then, is enter the competing domains into the Link Intersect tool (and your domain too).<\/p>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2139\" src=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"842\" height=\"504\" srcset=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool.png 842w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-67x40.png 67w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-134x80.png 134w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-50x30.png 50w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-100x60.png 100w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-40x24.png 40w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-80x48.png 80w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-30x18.png 30w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-60x36.png 60w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 842px) 100vw, 842px\" \/>\n<p>Ahrefs will show you all of the links that your competitors have, but your website doesn\u2019t.<\/p>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2140\" src=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1560\" height=\"759\" srcset=\"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-2.png 1560w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-2-1536x747.png 1536w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-2-82x40.png 82w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-2-164x80.png 164w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-2-62x30.png 62w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-2-123x60.png 123w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-2-49x24.png 49w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-2-99x48.png 99w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-2-37x18.png 37w, https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/M15-LBFLS-SFYC-link-intersect-tool-2-74x36.png 74w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1560px) 100vw, 1560px\" \/>\n<p>Simple!<\/p>\n<p>Needless to say, there are countless other link building tactics you can use, but it\u2019s impossible for us to go through each and every one of them in detail here &#8211; especially when there\u2019s lots of brilliant articles on link building, like this article from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.brightlocal.com\/blog\/5-local-link-building-tactics-try-2018\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">BrightLocal<\/a>.<\/p>\n"},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/modules\/2134"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/modules"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/module"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/modules\/2134\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2141,"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/modules\/2134\/revisions\/2141"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/modules\/418"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/susodigital.com\/textbook\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2134"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}